title: Another man dies fainting in a fuel queue  in Kadawatha
body_lines: Another senior citizen who fainted while standing in a fuel queue in Kadawatha has died on admission to hospital today.
Police said the 70-year-old victim, a three wheeler driver from Makola has died on admission to the Ragama Hospital.
A 71-year-old man also died yesterday on admission to hospital after fainting while standing in a fuel queue in Kandy town.(DSB)
